* Pirenne, Henri. &quot;The Stages in the Social History of Capitalism&quot;, &quot;The American Historical Review,&quot; 19:494, April 1914 in JSTOR
* Pirenne, Henri. &quot;Medieval Cities: Their Origins and the Revival of Trade&quot; (1927)
