* 1667 – Vera circuli et hyperbolae quadratura (&quot;The true squaring of the circle and hyperbola&quot;) via Internet Archive
* 1668 – &quot;Exercitationes geometricae&quot; (Geometrical exercises), link from Google Books.
* 1668 – &quot;Geometriae pars universalis&quot; (The universal part of geometry)

